ACCORDI IN MIDI
Accordo maggiore in MIDI
nota  ==  nota + 4  ==  nota + 7

          //ACCORDO MAGGIORE ON
          noteOn(midiCh, note + i, 127);  // channel, note, velocity
          MidiUSB.flush();
          noteOn(midiCh, note + 4 + i, 127);  // channel, note, velocity
          MidiUSB.flush();
          noteOn(midiCh, note + 7 + i, 127);  // channel, note, velocity
          MidiUSB.flush();

          //ACCORDO MAGGIORE OFF
          noteOn(midiCh, note + i, 0);  // channel, note, velocity
          MidiUSB.flush();
          noteOn(midiCh, note + 4 + i, 0);  // channel, note, velocity
          MidiUSB.flush();
          noteOn(midiCh, note + 7 + i, 0);  // channel, note, velocity
          MidiUSB.flush();


Accordo minore in MIDI
nota  ==  nota + 3  ==  nota + 7

          //ACCORDO MINORE ON
